title: Chicago Hope S04E19 - Objects Are Closer Than They Appear.avi
description:
Wilkes needs to figure out how a presumably healthy 15 year old dies, so her identical twin doesn't meet the same fate. A young friend of Kate's daughter is brought into the ER in cardiac arrest. The estranged brother of a comatose lesbian wants to make the medical decisions for her instead of her longtime partner. 



More to follow, please give back as much as you take.
